ygData.messageBody:
The gloves on the other hand give Enduring breath to you automatically (ie:
no clicking). A guildro suprised me with them late last week, and imagine
my suprise as we traveled underwater through LGuk and I got no Air Remaining
timer. I thought it was a bug at first ;o)~

-=B=-
